-lrb- cnn -rrb- the first trailer for a documentary on the life and music of late british singer amy winehouse was released thursday .
the teaser for `` amy : the girl behind the name , '' set for uk release on july 3 , features early footage of winehouse talking about how her music career was born and where she believed she was headed .
winehouse , known for her bluesy voice , bouffant hairdo and numerous tattoos , struggled publicly with drugs and alcohol during a career in which she recorded two albums and won six grammys -lrb- one posthumous -rrb- .
she died from alcohol poisoning at the age of 27 on july 23 , 2011 .